WEBVTT

00:05.000 --> 00:08.083
Previously on "Billions"...

00:08.166 --> 00:10.083
The only enemy
more dangerous

00:10.166 --> 00:13.083
than a man with
unlimited resources...

00:13.166 --> 00:13.959
is one
with nothing to lose.

00:14.041 --> 00:17.375
And that is what
you are looking at

00:17.458 --> 00:19.166
right here.

00:19.250 --> 00:21.000
This is for you...

00:21.083 --> 00:24.875
Look at them.
With that morning-after glow.

00:24.959 --> 00:28.000
This is what your wife
is out doing.

00:28.083 --> 00:29.000
You see things differently.

00:29.083 --> 00:31.625
That's an edge.
Congratulations.

00:31.709 --> 00:33.583
All the analysts
now answer to you.

00:33.667 --> 00:36.583
We've long suspected criminal
activity at Axe Capital.

00:36.667 --> 00:39.083
-Some parts of the job

00:39.166 --> 00:40.625
are pretty intuitive.

00:40.709 --> 00:42.458
Is there any law enforcement
here?

00:42.542 --> 00:43.667
No.

00:43.750 --> 00:46.542
You let me know
if any show up.

00:46.625 --> 00:49.542
-You should name a C.I.O.
-I'll do it.

00:49.625 --> 00:52.291
But I'm not running with you.
And neither are the kids.

00:52.375 --> 00:54.125
So, you do what you got to do,
but we're staying.

00:54.208 --> 00:56.333
Black Jack Foley.

00:56.417 --> 00:58.000
I'll be better

00:58.083 --> 01:01.041
if you help me out
with a little something.

01:01.125 --> 01:02.041
Jack.

01:02.125 --> 01:04.750
Will you make me governor?

01:06.291 --> 01:09.542
The Ice Juice IPO never tracks
back to my family,

01:09.625 --> 01:10.959
to my father's investment.

01:11.041 --> 01:13.458
Get out of the stock, Chuck.
They're gonna crush you.

01:13.542 --> 01:16.083
Wow, I'm glad to see
you view me as so defenseless.

01:16.166 --> 01:17.917
The Ice Juice short,
how do I get a piece of that?

01:18.000 --> 01:20.834
Ice Juice
never made anyone sick.

01:20.917 --> 01:21.792
You baited him?

01:21.875 --> 01:25.750
You used my company,
my career, my future...

01:25.834 --> 01:28.417
Where do you get
the fucking nerve?!

01:28.500 --> 01:29.834
I am done with you.

01:29.917 --> 01:30.750
You've been named
interim U.S. Attorney

01:30.834 --> 01:33.000
for the Eastern District.

01:33.083 --> 01:35.333
You didn't think this shit
happened by accident,

01:35.417 --> 01:36.667
did you, Mr. Dake?

01:36.750 --> 01:39.583
I've arranged that you'll lead
the prosecution at Eastern.

01:39.667 --> 01:40.917
Tell Sacker I'm gonna make
her Chief of Crim.

01:41.000 --> 01:44.709
I'm gonna find it.

01:44.792 --> 01:46.542
Whatever thread
you left behind.

01:46.625 --> 01:47.917
And I am gonna pull on it

01:48.000 --> 01:50.834
until your whole fucking world
unravels.

01:50.917 --> 01:52.792
I might go down behind
all of this,

01:52.875 --> 01:55.291
but you are gonna be
right there next to me.

01:56.709 --> 01:59.291
Worth it.

