02:56.834 --> 03:00.041
I'm from horse country,
Chuck, West Texas.

03:00.125 --> 03:03.250
My family bred 'em,
American quarterhorses.

03:03.333 --> 03:05.625
Those babies
fetch quite the price,

03:05.709 --> 03:08.208
so we were real gentle
with the product.

03:08.291 --> 03:09.417
We used teasers.

03:09.500 --> 03:11.458
Those are stallions
you put into the stall

03:11.542 --> 03:14.625
with the sole purpose of
making sure the mare's in heat,

03:14.709 --> 03:15.709
primed for breeding.

03:15.792 --> 03:17.208
Now, a teaser, he doesn't get
to do any fucking.

03:17.291 --> 03:20.000
He's just there
to get the mare ready.

03:20.083 --> 03:21.250
Take her kicks.

03:21.333 --> 03:24.083
Try to mount,
take some more kicks.

03:24.166 --> 03:25.750
By God, that teaser,

03:25.834 --> 03:29.250
he's got a rager going on
the whole dang time.

03:29.333 --> 03:30.959
But that doesn't matter.

03:31.041 --> 03:32.959
As soon as that dam
is ready,

03:33.041 --> 03:35.750
we yank that teaser out of
there, lead the real stud in,

03:35.834 --> 03:38.166
and he gets to do
all the fucking.

03:38.250 --> 03:42.291
Teaser has to make do with some
mangy hay and a bucket of oats.

03:42.375 --> 03:42.875
Brutal.

03:42.959 --> 03:47.583
Yeah, nature often is.

03:47.667 --> 03:50.291
Right now, you're
that teaser, aren't you,

03:50.375 --> 03:51.959
with Dake
prosecuting Axelrod?

03:52.041 --> 03:53.291
He's getting all the credit

03:53.375 --> 03:57.083
for putting the cuffs on him
and freezing his assets.

03:57.166 --> 04:00.166
Dake is fucking Axelrod
right now in front of everybody,

04:00.250 --> 04:02.250
and you,
you're back in the barn,

04:02.333 --> 04:05.583
nursing your rager
with a bucket of oats.

04:07.041 --> 04:08.166
Well, as long
as justice is served,

04:08.250 --> 04:10.500
credit doesn't matter
at all, General.

04:10.583 --> 04:12.917
Good.

04:13.000 --> 04:16.333
Why don't you tell me
how it really makes you feel

04:16.417 --> 04:19.458
to see Dake with the lariat
in his grip?

04:22.875 --> 04:25.709
You'd like to tear that case
from him with your bare hands

04:25.792 --> 04:27.500
and leave him crying
in the gutter.

04:27.583 --> 04:30.542
Hmm?

04:30.625 --> 04:32.291
You got some wolf in you,

04:32.375 --> 04:35.166
which is why
you're not getting fired.

04:35.250 --> 04:36.500
Not quite yet, anyway.

04:36.583 --> 04:39.000
No, sir, you are among
the blessed few.

04:39.083 --> 04:41.333
It's end times
for most of your brethren,

04:41.417 --> 04:44.083
but you have not been
raptured yet.

04:44.166 --> 04:45.834
I've only kept on
seven U.S. attorneys

04:45.917 --> 04:48.166
since the president
was good enough to appoint me

04:48.250 --> 04:49.458
Attorney General
of these United States.

04:49.542 --> 04:53.375
I just wanted to make sure
our agendas are aligned

04:53.458 --> 04:55.625
when it comes to
that justice you spoke of

04:55.709 --> 04:57.083
moments ago.

04:57.166 --> 05:00.458
These high-profile cases you
and your people have working?

05:00.542 --> 05:02.375
Heap of Wall Street-related
matters.

05:02.458 --> 05:05.333
Well, the markets
are within my purview.

05:05.417 --> 05:06.083
Well, that may be,

05:06.166 --> 05:08.000
but I come
from baseball country.

05:08.083 --> 05:10.583
We learn at an early age

05:10.667 --> 05:11.875
that a tie
goes to the runner.

05:11.959 --> 05:15.500
And that is how I want you to
think of our business community

05:15.583 --> 05:16.917
and its leaders
from now on.

05:17.000 --> 05:18.625
Now, look,
if there's a clear crime,

05:18.709 --> 05:20.500
then, by all means,
you go after it.

05:20.583 --> 05:24.458
But if it's a bang-bang play,
don't call a man out on a win.

05:24.542 --> 05:26.500
Just let that rally continue.

05:26.583 --> 05:30.417
I thought you come
from horse country.

05:33.542 --> 05:35.709
West Texas
contains multitudes, Chuck.

05:35.792 --> 05:37.792
Ahh.

05:37.875 --> 05:39.792
Prioritize the cases
that make sense.

05:39.875 --> 05:42.333
You know what to do
with the rest.

05:42.417 --> 05:45.834
They're marked
so there's no confusion.

05:47.875 --> 05:49.792
Come on, let's schottische on
into this ballroom.

05:49.875 --> 05:52.000
Come on.

