53:35.125 --> 53:38.125
What fantasies exactly?

53:38.208 --> 53:40.709
You being with other men.

53:44.458 --> 53:48.083
Of course.

53:48.166 --> 53:51.500
That's your  fantasy.

53:51.583 --> 53:53.875
You're that pathetic,
