53:54.709 --> 53:57.667
I am. I am.

53:57.750 --> 53:59.709
I want to hear
about you and--

53:59.792 --> 54:00.834
Young men?

54:00.917 --> 54:05.625
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

54:05.709 --> 54:09.458
Um...

54:09.542 --> 54:11.291
will he be handsome, rich?

54:11.375 --> 54:12.917
-Of course.

54:13.000 --> 54:14.000
